  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Um, at the-- sometime in June, again, like I mentioned before, we got note that there was going to be a big razia in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Um, again, the underground came, or someone warned my parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was a real big one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All over the whole city, nobody could get in or out, or, you know, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We lived, um, like I say, at the house, a three-story house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "However, under the house was a crawl space, maybe 2 feet high.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we knew about the crawl space, and we had been there before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- so we moved in the crawl space.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was right at the-- when you come into the building was a deck, you know, under the carpet where you could move in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We moved into there, and we lived there for a couple days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, mother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, the neighbors on the second floor knew because they brought us food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kind of, you know, when there was nothing, they kind of hit the little deck what was, you know, the opening or the cover, and then we knew there was someone there that wanted to-- you know.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Till finally-- I don't say we have been in there maybe one or two days-- they finally moved to the house where we are, were.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you could see them come because the crawl space had to be vented and aired.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the German boots was right in front of the crawl space, and we was on the other side of the grill.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had the standing there, SS or whatever it was, with the gun and all this.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
